  "texts": [
    "Data integration is critical to DL applications in IoT-based bio-and medical informatics.",
    "It involves combining multiple data sources from various sensors, devices, and databases into a unified dataset that can be used to train and test DL models.",
    "In medical informatics, the data sources may include EHR, medical imaging data, clinical notes, and genomic data.",
    "Different systems may generate these data sources and may have different formats, making integration challenging.",
    "However, integrating these data sources is essential to capture the full complexity of the patient's health status."
  ],
